{"type": "article", "id": 28927, "title": "茶几系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-30T06:55:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123444i4tM9zLKsdQ7jhvY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>设计师 <a href=\"http://www.danielgarciasanchez.com/\">Daniel Garcia</a> 近日为 <a href=\"https://woodendot.com/en/\">Woodendot</a> 设计了一套名为 Batea 的茶几系列。这些大小不一的茶几均由橡木制成，边缘则采用了圆弧形的设计，带给人一种柔和温暖的感觉。每一款茶几都可以通过调整组装结合成不同的家具组合，适用于不同的室内环境。Garcia 为大号和中号茶几还设计了储物空间，只需要将上层桌面推开就可以存放小物或者是装饰品。这是它的<a href=\"https://woodendot.com/en/product-category/tables/\">购买链接</a>，售价从 199 到 449 欧元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123442vEubJagwmU8iZnRD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123442xepHfER8kzGFSc5r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123443dDtr9sB8G0iKyqkQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123443ufKUDgMG8RxtVw5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56356968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}